Set up a Premium Workspace using Embedded (pbipremiumexperimentalcapacity) the name for the Worspace should be your Initials+PipelinesBC_DEV
Create deployment pipeline in that workspace
Publish report to workspace
Deploy to Test
Change the dataset and publish the report
Publish changes to Test (you cant see what changed only that i did change)
Deploy to PROD
Change the Datasource of the Dataset with Data source rules (you have to use parameter Rules) 
Check the dataset in Prod 
Redeploy to Prod and check again
